Name: Get-AppvVirtualProcess
Synopsis: Displays the virtual processes running on a computer.

Name: Start-AppvVirtualProcess
Synopsis: Starts a virtual process.

Name: Add-AppvClientConnectionGroup
Synopsis: Creates a composition of multiple packages.

Name: Add-AppvClientPackage
Synopsis: Adds a package to a computer running the App-V client.

Name: Add-AppvPublishingServer
Synopsis: Adds a publishing server for the computer that runs the App-V client.

Name: Disable-Appv
Synopsis: Disables the App-V service.

Name: Disable-AppvClientConnectionGroup
Synopsis: Disables a connection group on the computer running the App-V client.

Name: Enable-Appv
Synopsis: Enables the App-V service.

Name: Enable-AppvClientConnectionGroup
Synopsis: Enables a running connection group on the computer running the App-V client.

Name: Get-AppvClientApplication
Synopsis: Returns applications that are part of App-V Client Packages.

Name: Get-AppvClientConfiguration
Synopsis: Returns the configuration for the App-V client.

Name: Get-AppvClientConnectionGroup
Synopsis: Returns an App-V connection group object.

Name: Get-AppvClientMode
Synopsis: Displays the mode for the App-V Client.

Name: Get-AppvClientPackage
Synopsis: Returns App-V Client Packages.

Name: Get-AppvPublishingServer
Synopsis: Returns App-V Server objects.

Name: Get-AppvStatus
Synopsis: Gets the status of the App-V service.

Name: Mount-AppvClientConnectionGroup
Synopsis: Streams the contents of packages to the local disk.

Name: Mount-AppvClientPackage
Synopsis: Loads a package into the App-V cache.

Name: Publish-AppvClientPackage
Synopsis: Publishes the App-V package.

Name: Remove-AppvClientConnectionGroup
Synopsis: Deletes an App-V connection group on the client.

Name: Remove-AppvClientPackage
Synopsis: Removes the package from a computer.

Name: Remove-AppvPublishingServer
Synopsis: Removes an App-V publishing server.

Name: Repair-AppvClientConnectionGroup
Synopsis: Resets the user package settings for the connection group.

Name: Repair-AppvClientPackage
Synopsis: Resets the user settings of a package.

Name: Send-AppvClientReport
Synopsis: Sends reporting data from the client.

Name: Set-AppvClientConfiguration
Synopsis: Applies configuration settings to the App-V Client.

Name: Set-AppvClientMode
Synopsis: Sets the mode in which the client runs.

Name: Set-AppvClientPackage
Synopsis: Configures an App-V Client Package.

Name: Set-AppvPublishingServer
Synopsis: Modifies properties of an App-V Publishing Server.

Name: Stop-AppvClientConnectionGroup
Synopsis: Shuts down the shared virtual environment of a connection group.

Name: Stop-AppvClientPackage
Synopsis: Shuts down virtual environments for specified packages.

Name: Sync-AppvPublishingServer
Synopsis: Initiates the App-V Publishing Refresh operation.

Name: Unpublish-AppvClientPackage
Synopsis: Removes the extension points for packages.
